node.text:
YO! It's  GIVEAWAY time! Ya'll already know my hairstyle is iconic, but now I wanna see how it looks on YOU! First, follow @got2bUSA, then post a pic to your feed of you rockin your own version of my style with your most gravity-defying spikes, blowouts, mohawks, whatever ya got! Make sure to tag @djpaulyd & @got2busa! Let your creativity flow and one lucky winner will get hooked up with my Limited Edition göt2b Blasting Freeze Spray & Styling Spiking Glue, the classic göt2b Blasting Freeze Spray & Styling Spiking glue, plus a custom shirt signed by me, ya' boy DJ Pauly D! One Entry Per Person! 

* NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Open to all legal residents of, and physically located within, the 50 US/DC, age 18+. Void outside 50 US/DC and where prohibited. Ends 7/26/2021 at 11:59PM ET. For full Official Rules visit: https://bit.ly/PaulyDgot2bTC
